# Claude Code local state
# - settings.local.json is per-user permissions; never share.
# - context/sessions is per-user mid-session checkpoints written by
#   the `context-save` skill. Keep private by default — if a team
#   wants to share them, remove the line and commit explicitly.
.claude/settings.local.json
.context/sessions/
